<h2 class="bold font-l">We Are The Giants Now...</h2>
<p class="_pmvv-vidbox-descTxt">
Following the end of the Human-Covenant War, Humanity has managed to grow and expand technologically to become closer to what their predecessors 100,000 years ago were at. </p>
<p class='example_row'>Example of:<br><a href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/FlauntingYourFleets" class='trope-example-link'>Flaunting Your Fleets</a></p>
</div>
